-- Argentine Truckersâ€™ Strike Blocks Fuel Refineries, Infobae Says
-- B y   R o d r i g o   O r i h u e l a
-- 2012-06-20T12:33:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-20/argentine-truckers-strike-blocks-fuel-refineries-infobae-says.html
Argentine truckers are blocking the
entrance to oil refineries and fuel distribution plants after
starting a three day strike today to demand higher salaries,
news website Infobae  reported .  Workers continued with the strike even after the Labor
Ministry issued an order to hold compulsory salary talks for 15
days, Infobae reported, without saying where it got the
information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
